Exploring Markdown

On this project I will be exploring palmerpenguins dataset. We will focus on exploring the body mass of penguins.

We can see that the penguins body mass mean was 4202 grams, with the lowest body mass at 2700 grams and the highest at 6300 grams.

Part 2

On this section we will explore the body mass of the penguins, looking at a histogram for normal distribution, a boxplot for homogenity of variance, and a plot graph.

hist(penguins$body_mass_g)

boxplot(penguins$body_mass_g)

plot(penguins$body_mass_g)

From the histogram and boxplot we can see that the penguins body mass was slightly right skewed.
